COMMITTEE REPORT
Mr. Speaker: Your Committee on Judiciary, to which was referred
House Bill 1036, has had the same under consideration and begs leave
to report the same back to the House with the recommendation that said
bill be amended as follows:
Page 1, line 3, delete "(a) Before the department" and insert "The
department shall have direct in-person contact with an alleged
victim of child abuse or neglect not more than thirty (30) days
before the department:
(1) concludes an assessment under IC 31-33; or
(2) dismisses or terminates a child in need of services case
pending before a juvenile court.".
Page 1, delete lines 4 through 12.
and when so amended that said bill do pass.
(Reference is to HB 1036 as introduced.)
